Stay updated with the latest Night Teer results instantly! Get first and second round results directly in your browser.

Designed specifically for Night Teer enthusiasts, this extension allows you to access the latest results without navigating away from your current tab.

Key Features:

- Instant Updates: Fetch the latest results for both the first and second rounds of Night Teer directly from the official source.
- Easy Access: View results instantly with a single click on the extension icon in your toolbar.
- Simple Layout: Enjoy a clean and organized interface displaying the results along with their respective times.
- Background Color: Results are highlighted with a soothing background color for easy visibility.
- Date Display: Know when the results were published with a clear date display.
Whether you're a regular player or a curious observer, this extension is your go-to tool for keeping up with Night Teer results effortlessly. Download now and never miss a result again!"
